{"article_id":"3Wd4NHepyvayB9gQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The mission","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"to rescue 12 Thai boys and their soccer coach","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"who had been trapped in a cave in northern Thailand for over two weeks","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"is just about over .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"As of Tuesday morning , all 12 boys and their coach had been brought out of the cave by the team of expert divers","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"deployed","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"to help guide the boys along the 2.5-mile journey to safety .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The boys are in good overall health ,","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"according to the Ministry of Public Health .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"On Saturday , June 23 , a group of 12 boys between the ages of 11 and 16 went with their soccer coach to explore a cave in the Tham Luang Nang Non cave system .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"As they entered ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"rain picked up ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"and the rising water trapped them inside .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The group of 13 was missing for nine days","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"before they were discovered by two British divers .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"People in Thailand and around the world rejoiced","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"when the group was found ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"but there was another problem :","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"getting them out .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Some sections of the cave were fully submerged in water","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"and the journey seemed treacherous for the boys , aged 11 to 16 .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Rescuers began to frantically pump water out of the cave ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"while oxygen levels in the cave began to drop on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"As the threat of more rains","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"that could further flood the cave","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"loomed ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"a rescue mission","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to get the team ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"whose nickname is the Wild Boars ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"out of the cave","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"began in earnest on Sunday morning .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"At least 13 specialist divers and five Thai Navy SEALS were sent in","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"escort the boys and their coach out .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"' s Radhika Viswanathan has a full explainer on the situation here .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"On Sunday , four boys were saved ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"and after a pause on Sunday evening , a second phase of the mission commenced","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to attempt to rescue the others .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Four more were rescued Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"and the mission resumed Tuesday morning ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"when the final four boys and their coach were brought out of the cave .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"Here ' s what else we know :","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"The mission","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to rescue the 12 boys and their soccer coach from a cave in northern Thailand","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"began at 10 am local time Sunday .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Thirteen specialist divers and five Thai Navy SEALS were sent","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"to try to reach the boys","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and get them out .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"The plan is to pair each person","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"being rescued","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"with two divers ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"fit them with a facemask","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"connected to an air tank ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"and escort them out .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"The Thai Navy SEAL ' s Facebook page confirmed on Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"that all 12 boys and the coach had been saved .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"\" We are not sure","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"if this is a miracle , a science , or what .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"All the thirteen Wild Boars are now out of the cave , \"","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"it said .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Chiang Rai acting Gov . Narongsak Osatanakorn ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"who is leading the rescue operation ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"said at a news conference","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that efforts went \" much better","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"than expected \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"and that the healthiest people were taken out first .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"A second phase of the operation started at 11 am local time on Monday","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"and involved many of the same divers .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Four more boys were retrieved on Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"putting the total of boys rescued at eight .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"The mission is on pause again .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"The coach taught the boys to meditate inside the cave","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"to help them stay calm .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Part of the operation ' s success hinged on whether monsoon rains pick up again .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"According to the New York Times ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"rain won ' t immediately make water levels rise in the cave ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"but it will make matters even more urgent .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"The route","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"the boys and divers needed to travel","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to get out of the cave","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"was 2.5 miles from the cave entrance ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and portions of it are submerged ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"but not all .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"It takes experienced divers about five hours to make the trip .","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"The escape route is fraught :","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"A former Thai Navy SEAL , 38-year-old Saman Gunan , died on Friday","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"while trying to reach the group with oxygen .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"The boys and their coach have been trapped in the cave since Saturday , June 23 ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"and they were discovered on Monday , July 2 .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"It was initially thought they might be able to wait out monsoon season in the cave ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"but dropping oxygen levels have caused concern .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"An air pipe has been run from the rescue base inside the cave to the chamber","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"where the boys and their coach are located ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"about 2.5 miles from the mouth of the cave .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The last people","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"to emerge from the cave at 10pm local time","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"were the doctor","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"who has been caring for them since they were first discovered last Monday","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"and three Thai Navy Seals","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"involved in the rescue operation .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":197,"left":107,"right":196,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":102,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":0,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":4,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":137,"right":195,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":130,"right":136,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":112,"right":129,"relati